title: TUESDAY 4/20 - NFL DRAFT TRADE BREWING?
itunes:title: TUESDAY 4/20 - NFL DRAFT TRADE BREWING?
description:
The Dolphins receiving trade interest in their 6th overall pick (0:06) as teams are looking to move up in the upcoming draft. Trey Lance (0:36) held his second pro day workout on Monday. Quarterback Alex Smith (1:01) announces his retirement after 16 seasons in the NFL. Patrick Mahomes (2:33) gives us an update on his injured toe
